The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Hurst named Match Referee

 - ODIs vs WI, Lanka 

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: Alan Hurst, of the elite panel, would be the Match Referee for Indias eight ODIs at home against the West Indies and Sri Lanka, according to an ICC statement on Wednesday. 

While Billy Bowden will be the neutral umpire for Indias first four ODIs against the Caribbeans, Simon Taufel will officiate in the last four ODIs against the visiting Sri Lankans, the statement read. 




